{"name": "test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_aggregated", "status": "passed", "description": "\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries using SGLang.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and an SGLang worker\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n    ", "attachments": [{"name": "log", "source": "d1650786-9005-4d26-aee7-1ff44fd059ad-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stdout", "source": "a4b2f4de-0d11-43c9-8cfe-f3094a92ec80-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stderr", "source": "c9361f89-5074-48cc-892e-9956c2118f9a-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}], "parameters": [{"name": "framework", "value": "'sglang'"}, {"name": "platform", "value": "'amd64'"}, {"name": "test_type", "value": "'pre_merge_gpu'"}], "start": 1775682251817, "stop": 1775682358002, "uuid": "49c685e9-72d7-4622-9fe8-fafe87fea2b6", "historyId": "bbd81b53358882e5d0d4fde41e835bac", "testCaseId": "9a8b2f4387f6c64cbead2a68dc13096e", "fullName": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_sglang#test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_aggregated", "labels": [{"name": "dynamo_workflow", "value": "Nightly CI Pipeline"}, {"name": "dynamo_framework", "value": "sglang"}, {"name": "dynamo_platform", "value": "amd64"}, {"name": "dynamo_testType", "value": "pre_merge_gpu"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "nightly"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "e2e"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "gpu_1"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "fault_tolerance"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "sglang"}, {"name": "parentSuite", "value": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha"}, {"name": "suite", "value": "test_sglang"}, {"name": "host", "value": "prod-tester-amd-gpu-v1-phg7c-runner-pmrns"}, {"name": "thre